---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import TrustedByCarousel from '../components/home/TrustedByCarousel';
import GlobeSection from '../components/home/GlobeSection';
import { MagneticCTA } from '../components/ui/magnetic-cta';
import { TextReveal } from '../components/ui/text-reveal';
import { BackgroundMesh } from '../components/ui/background-paper-shaders';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Meet the team behind Duddcash — video & photo production for brands, artists, and events.">
  <section class="about section">
    <!-- Floating 3D icons -->
    <div class="film-icon film-icon--1">
      <img src="/icons/camera.png" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="film-icon film-icon--2">
      <img src="/icons/film-camera.png" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="film-icon film-icon--3">
      <img src="/icons/clapperboard.png" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="film-icon film-icon--4">
      <img src="/icons/director-chair.png" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="film-icon film-icon--5">
      <img src="/icons/film-camera.png" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="film-icon film-icon--6">
      <img src="/icons/clapperboard.png" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="film-icon film-icon--7">
      <img src="/icons/camera.png" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="film-icon film-icon--8">
      <img src="/icons/director-chair.png" alt="" />
    </div>

    <div class="about__inner">
      <div class="about__header" data-animate>
        <h1 class="about__title">Our Story</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="about__text" data-animate>
        <p>
          At the age of 15, Calo Shiban picked up his first video camera. Instantly, he knew, nothing else could match the feeling of creating the exact shot you saw in your head. Over the course of the next year, he poured over hundreds of movies, and tried his best to apply what he saw to his short films. Using his digital media class as a springboard, he created countless short stories, and comedic segments alongside his best friend Anthony Arutyunov. Their teacher, Mr. Bokovitz, loved the work the two created together and introduced them to a former student (Ben Gugick), who excelled at short form advertisements mostly featured on Instagram. Ben presented them and the rest of the class with a variety of well shot, well paced, and well edited creative edits. Calo was enamored with the work and stayed for nearly an hour after class asking Ben how he created such incredible visuals with a seemingly shoe-string budget. Ben loved discussing all the intricacies of his craft and urged Calo to give him a call after school. After some initial hesitation, Calo called him a few months later hoping to learn as much as he could about the world of videography &amp; editing.
        </p>

        <input type="checkbox" id="story-toggle" class="story__checkbox" />
        <div class="story__more">
          <p>
            During the following summer, Ben taught Calo as much as he could about his approach to content creation. Shortly after, Anthony asked Calo to set up an introduction to learn the craft as well. Guided by Ben, the two picked up several small marketing jobs in Cleveland and worked with Ben as much as possible to develop their skills as well as build their own brand. Anthony understood the assignment almost immediately and within months seemed like a seasoned veteran in the editing field. Calo tried his best to keep up on the editing front, while also pulling weight through client discussions and camera direction. Despite making less than $10 an hour on most jobs, the competitive nature between Anthony and Calo pushed them to continue down the rabbit hole of instagram marketing. When one of them made a video that was a cut above the rest, the other immediately started working harder to catch up.
          </p>
          <p>
            While the work they did varied greatly from project to project, the duo established themselves as some of the best nightlife creators in Cleveland before they had graduated high school. Shortly before the end of their high school education and the journey into college, an opportunity presented itself that could turn their small money passion projects into a full time job. Ben was contacted by the largest night club in Cleveland, FWD, and they hoped to have him on board for the entire summer. Headlined by artists like Machine Gun Kelly, John Summit, and Dom Dolla, FWD promised an action packed summer with full creative control over the content. The only problem was, Ben had already made plans to move his business to Chicago and start down a new path. Because of this, Ben recommended Calo and Anthony fill his role as lead shooters and editors with the condition that he would oversee all of the edits to ensure their quality was at the highest level possible. FWD management agreed, noting their shock to learn that both members of DUDDCASH had not even turned 18 yet.
          </p>
          <p>
            To maintain the jobs they already had, continue to build relationships with the clients Ben was leaving behind, and make their parents happy, Calo and Anthony decided to commit to a year of in-person education at Cleveland State University. Both of them hoped by the end of that year their business would flourish and they could re-evaluate their need for college and Cleveland as a whole. But before they thought about that, they needed to deliver for FWD. Just as before, the duo traded off edits hoping to one up the other every weekend. Within the first month, the marketing team felt more than happy with their decision and the growing sentiment was that DUDDCASH got better with every edit. They balanced FWD with 3 other night life venues as well as whatever job requests came their way to have as productive and high paying a summer as possible. Every pay check that came in went straight back into the business. New cameras, new computers, ND filters, gimbals, lenses. As they got better, so did their tools.
          </p>
          <p>
            It was the following year at Cleveland State where the business would undergo a staggering amount of change in a relatively short period of time. While moving in to their tiny dorm room, they met a content creator named Gabe who would be rooming right across the hall from Calo and Anthony. Just as Ben had done for them, they tried their best to coach Gabe to become a better editor. Not long after they brought on another college freshman, Logan, who brought drone operation and great shooting to the table. While their team grew, Calo and Anthony tried their best to be students first. What quickly became apparent was, the work they were doing was much more important than the degree. Thus, when it was time to work on an edit for a Coachella after party with only 3-days to turn it around, college was pushed to the back burner. This move paid dividends as it led to a connection with a producer who offered a plethora of quick-turn movie premiere edits. From the time they got the footage, the edit would need to be completed within 24 hours. The result? Pressure formed diamonds. It was a shock for the both of them to learn that when they worked under extreme pressure off very few hours of sleep, they were able to make some of their best work. By the end of the school year it seemed like things couldn't get any better. Their work was nearly unrecognizable from just 6 months prior, let alone their first summer at FWD. On top of that, their income had finally started to match the effort they were putting in. Then, in June of 2024, they would make their best connection yet.
          </p>
          <p>
            YadaYada Studio, led by Maddi Clarke, specializes in social media content collaborations with high level brands. The pacing of the videos was usually a bit slower, and more focused on the shooting and product than the content DUDDCASH usually made. Nonetheless, Maddi reached out to the boys hoping to start them out on a small job with Lululemon. Calo and Anthony loved working for Maddi and the feeling was mutual as they got brought on for more and more work. This work proved to be important as it helped the boys improve their shooting leaps and bounds as editing had become more and more important for them. This piece of the puzzle allowed Calo and Anthony to make their next big step, joining Ben in Chicago.
          </p>
          <p>
            Having trained Gabe and Logan to the best of their abilities, DUDDCASH left the two with every connection in Cleveland they had and moved cities. Their college trainees remain huge parts of the business and often help out on work that needs multiple sets of hands.
          </p>
        </div>
        <label for="story-toggle" class="story__toggle">
          <span class="story__toggle-open">Read the full story</span>
          <span class="story__toggle-close">Collapse story</span>
          <svg class="story__toggle-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" />
          </svg>
        </label>
      </div>

    </div>

  </section>

  <!-- Our Goal -->
  <section class="our-goal" data-animate>
    <div class="our-goal__content">
      <h2 class="our-goal__label">Our Goal</h2>
      <p class="our-goal__text">Keep growing as filmmakers while stepping into more of a directing role — with our team behind it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Scroll indicator after Our Goal -->
  <div class="scroll-hint scroll-hint--after-goal" data-animate>
    <svg width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
      <path d="M7 13l5 5 5-5" /><path d="M7 6l5 5 5-5" />
    </svg>
  </div>

  <!-- Team Zone — unified background wrapper -->
  <section class="team-zone">
    <!-- Subtle shader background -->
    <div class="team-zone__shader">
      <BackgroundMesh
        client:visible
        speed={0.15}
        colors={["#b0a99e", "#9e978c", "#8a8378", "#a09890"]}
        style={{ position: "absolute", inset: 0, width: "100%", height: "100%" }}
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Soft radial glow behind cards -->
    <div class="team-zone__glow"></div>

    <!-- Meet the Team divider -->
    <section class="meet-team" data-animate>
      <div class="meet-team__inner">
        <div class="meet-team__line"></div>
        <h2 class="meet-team__heading">Meet the Team</h2>
        <div class="meet-team__line"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Founders -->
    <section class="founders section">
      <div class="founders__inner">
        <div class="founders__grid" data-animate>
          <div class="founders__card">
            <span class="founders__card-border"></span>
            <div class="founders__card-content">
              <div class="founders__avatar">
                <span class="founders__initials">AA</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="founders__name">Anthony Arutyunov</h3>
              <span class="founders__role">Co-Founder</span>
              <span class="founders__specialty">Director / Editor</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="founders__card">
            <span class="founders__card-border"></span>
            <div class="founders__card-content">
              <div class="founders__avatar">
                <span class="founders__initials">CS</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="founders__name">Calo Shiban</h3>
              <span class="founders__role">Co-Founder</span>
              <span class="founders__specialty">Director / Editor</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team -->
    <section class="team section">
      <div class="team__inner">
        <div class="team__grid" data-animate>
          <div class="team__card">
            <div class="team__avatar">
              <span class="team__initials">GD</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="team__name">Gabriel Delgado</h4>
          </div>

          <div class="team__card team__card--featured">
            <div class="team__avatar">
              <span class="team__initials">LM</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="team__name">Logan Murray</h4>
            <p class="team__bio">Traveling videographer, editor and drone pilot passionate about putting quality first. Built his career on nightlife and has since expanded to cover almost every niche — with notable collaborations including Myles Garrett and Tee Higgins, plus nightclubs across the country from Miami to Las Vegas.</p>
            <div class="team__links">
              <a href="https://www.instagram.com/loganmurrayproductions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="team__link">IG: @loganmurrayproductions</a>
              <span class="team__email">loganmurrayproduction@gmail.com</span>
            </div>
            <div class="team__signature">
              <img src="/logan-murray-signature.png" alt="Logan Murray signature" class="team__signature-img" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="team__card">
            <div class="team__avatar">
              <span class="team__initials">JJ</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="team__name">Jayden Jones</h4>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Scroll indicator to Globe -->
    <div class="scroll-hint scroll-hint--team-bottom" data-animate>
      <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="M7 13l5 5 5-5" /><path d="M7 6l5 5 5-5" />
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Globe -->
  <GlobeSection client:visible />

  <!-- Trusted By -->
  <TrustedByCarousel client:visible />

  <!-- Ready to Work — bordered container -->
  <section class="about-cta-section">
    <div class="about-cta-card">
      <div class="about-cta-card__border"></div>
      <div class="about-cta-card__inner">
        <!-- Shader background -->
        <div class="about-cta-card__shader">
          <BackgroundMesh
            client:visible
            speed={0.2}
            colors={["#e8e4dc", "#d4cfc6", "#c8c0b4", "#ddd8cf"]}
            style={{ position: "absolute", inset: 0, width: "100%", height: "100%" }}
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Grid overlay -->
        <svg class="about-cta-card__grid" width="100%" height="100%">
          <defs>
            <pattern id="cta-grid" width="40" height="40" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
              <path d="M 40 0 L 0 0 0 40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" />
            </pattern>
          </defs>
          <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#cta-grid)" />
        </svg>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="about-cta-card__content" data-animate>
          <TextReveal
            client:visible
            text="Ready to work together?"
            staggerDelay={0.1}
            initialDelay={0.1}
            style={{
              fontFamily: "var(--font-display)",
              fontSize: "clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.5rem)",
              fontWeight: 500,
              letterSpacing: "-0.025em",
              lineHeight: 1.1,
              color: "var(--color-text)",
            }}
          />
          <p class="about-cta-card__sub">No fluff. Just sharp creative, fast turnarounds, and work that speaks.</p>
          <div class="about-cta-card__buttons">
            <MagneticCTA client:visible href="/contact">Start a Project</MagneticCTA>
            <MagneticCTA client:visible href="/#portfolio">See the Work</MagneticCTA>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    position: relative;
    padding-top: clamp(2.5rem, 5vh, 4rem);
    padding-bottom: clamp(1rem, 2vh, 1.5rem);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about__inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(2rem, 6vw, 7rem);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about__header {
    margin-bottom: clamp(1.5rem, 3vh, 2.5rem);
  }

  .about__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-text);
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: clamp(0.8rem, 1.5vh, 1.2rem);
  }

  .about__title::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 48px;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(160, 140, 110, 0.7), transparent);
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  .about__text {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .about__text p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.9;
    letter-spacing: 0.005em;
  }

  .about__text p + p {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  /* Story expand toggle */
  .story__checkbox {
    display: none;
  }

  .story__more {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .story__checkbox:checked ~ .story__more {
    max-height: 4000px;
  }

  .story__checkbox:checked ~ .story__toggle .story__toggle-open {
    display: none;
  }

  .story__checkbox:checked ~ .story__toggle .story__toggle-close {
    display: inline;
  }

  .story__checkbox:checked ~ .story__toggle .story__toggle-icon {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .story__toggle {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding: 10px 22px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(160, 140, 110, 0.25);
    background: rgba(160, 140, 110, 0.06);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .story__toggle:hover {
    border-color: rgba(160, 140, 110, 0.45);
    background: rgba(160, 140, 110, 0.1);
  }

  .story__toggle-open,
  .story__toggle-close {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: #444;
  }

  .story__toggle-close {
    display: none;
  }

  .story__toggle-icon {
    color: rgba(140, 120, 90, 0.6);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  /* ─── Our Goal ─── */
  .our-goal {
    padding: clamp(1rem, 2vh, 1.5rem) clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 4rem);
  }

  .our-goal__content {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    background: #0b0b0b;
    border-radius: 23px;
    padding: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem) clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);
  }

  .our-goal__label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .our-goal__text {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    max-width: 480px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Floating 3D icons */
  .film-icon {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .film-icon img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    opacity: 0.95;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1));
  }

  /* DSLR camera — top right */
  .film-icon--1 {
    width: 70px;
    top: 8%;
    right: 6%;
    animation: floatIcon1 9s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  /* Vintage film camera — left side */
  .film-icon--2 {
    width: 55px;
    top: 32%;
    left: 4%;
    animation: floatIcon2 11s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  /* Clapperboard — right mid */
  .film-icon--3 {
    width: 48px;
    bottom: 28%;
    right: 10%;
    animation: floatIcon3 13s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  /* Director chair — bottom left */
  .film-icon--4 {
    width: 45px;
    bottom: 12%;
    left: 10%;
    animation: floatIcon1 8s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }

  /* Film camera small — top left */
  .film-icon--5 {
    width: 38px;
    top: 12%;
    left: 12%;
    animation: floatIcon3 10s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }

  /* Clapperboard small — bottom right */
  .film-icon--6 {
    width: 35px;
    bottom: 6%;
    right: 5%;
    animation: floatIcon2 12s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  /* Camera small — mid left */
  .film-icon--7 {
    width: 42px;
    top: 60%;
    left: 3%;
    animation: floatIcon1 14s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  /* Director chair small — top center-right */
  .film-icon--8 {
    width: 32px;
    top: 5%;
    right: 28%;
    animation: floatIcon2 9s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }

  @keyframes floatIcon1 {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-12px) rotate(3deg); }
  }

  @keyframes floatIcon2 {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
    50% { transform: translateY(10px) rotate(-2deg); }
  }

  @keyframes floatIcon3 {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
    33% { transform: translateY(-8px) rotate(4deg); }
    66% { transform: translateY(6px) rotate(-3deg); }
  }

  /* Scroll hint chevrons */
  .scroll-hint {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: clamp(2rem, 4vh, 3rem) 0 clamp(1rem, 2vh, 1.5rem);
    color: var(--color-muted);
    opacity: 0.35;
    animation: scrollBounce 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes scrollBounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.35; }
    50% { transform: translateY(6px); opacity: 0.6; }
  }

  .scroll-hint--after-goal {
    padding: 0 0 clamp(3rem, 5vh, 4rem);
    opacity: 0.5;
    animation: scrollBounceTeam 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .scroll-hint--team-bottom {
    padding: clamp(1rem, 2vh, 1.5rem) 0 clamp(3rem, 5vh, 4rem);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .scroll-hint--team-bottom svg {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
  }

  @keyframes scrollBounceTeam {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.5; }
    50% { transform: translateY(8px); opacity: 0.8; }
  }

  .scroll-hint--team-bottom {
    animation: scrollBounceTeam 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  /* ─── Team Zone — unified background ─── */
  .team-zone {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    background: #403D39;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .team-zone .scroll-hint {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  .team-zone__shader {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    opacity: 0.25;
  }

  .team-zone__glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 35%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 60%;
    height: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
    filter: blur(60px);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .team-zone .meet-team,
  .team-zone .founders,
  .team-zone .team {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
  }

  /* Meet the Team divider */
  .meet-team {
    padding: clamp(6rem, 10vh, 8rem) 0 clamp(2rem, 4vh, 3rem);
  }

  .meet-team__inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(2rem, 6vw, 7rem);
  }

  .meet-team__line {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), transparent);
  }

  .meet-team__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.4rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: #fff;
    white-space: nowrap;
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .meet-team__heading::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(200, 175, 130, 0.6), transparent);
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  /* ─── Founders ─── */
  .founders {
    padding: clamp(1rem, 2vh, 2rem) 0 clamp(2rem, 3vh, 3rem);
  }

  .founders__inner {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(2rem, 6vw, 7rem);
  }


  .founders__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem);
  }

  .founders__card {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Animated gradient border — appears on hover */
  .founders__card-border {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 1.5px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2),
